// Features of java 8

1. Lambda Expression -> It is used to initialize functional Interface in java
2. Stream API -> Java Stream Api for bulk data operations on collections.
3. Date and Time API -> Under the package of java.time java 8 offers new date time API.

4. Base64 Encode Decode
5. Method reference and constructor reference ->  :: operator
6. Default and static method in interface

7. Functional Interface
8. Optional class
9. Java IO improvement
10. Collections API improvement
